Web3 Micro-Insurance L1
Overview

Web3 Micro-Insurance L1 enables affordable, on-demand insurance coverage for small-scale risks.

Features
On-demand insurance policies
Low-cost coverage models
Automated claim payouts
Risk pooling mechanisms
Transparent policy management
Architecture
Policy Registry

Stores insurance contracts.

Risk Engine

Evaluates micro-risk scenarios.

Claims Module

Processes and validates claims.

Liquidity Pool

Maintains insurance reserves.

Use Cases
Travel micro-insurance
Device protection
Gig worker coverage
Short-term insurance
